tial Coordinates; Multi-source-Domain Adaptation for TMS-EEG Based Depression Detection; Structured Dialogue System for Mental Health: An LLM Chatbot Leveraging the PM+ Guidelines; feature Extraction Method Based on Contrastive Learning for Dysarthria Detection; flying Together with Audio and Video: Enhancing Communication for the Hearing-Impaired Through an Emerging Closed Captioning Standard.
