TI  - I can't join, but I will send my agent: Stand-in enhanced asynchronous meetings (SEAM)
AU  - Bai, Zhongyi
AU  - Grønbæk, Jens Emil Sloth
AU  - Irlitti, Andrew
AU  - Knibbe, Jarrod
AU  - Velloso, Eduardo
